<tr><td><font face="Comic Sans MS" size=2>From Fletch:<br><br>Before the latest two patches, the level 43 Bard song, a mana using AoE damage song called &quot;Denon's Desperate Dirge&quot;, damaged the bard as well as surrounding mobs. This has been fixed. The song will no longer damage the bard when sung. I tried it against two mobs, they each took 288 points of non-melee damage, while my health bar remained unaffected.<br><br>Thanks! <br></font></td></tr>
